The problem in the code is that "score" property of "profile" record does n
not exist. It should be "points". So, the correct program to fix it would b
be as follows:

```tundra
val raw = {
  profile: {
    name: "Ada",
    score: 12
   }
};

val profile = raw.profile;
val selected = {
  points: profile.score
};

print(selected.points);
```
